es at the foot of the 2,096m Kebnetkaise massif. Several guests had caught the bug in recent days but it was also detected in hikers camping in the area.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sun, 06 Aug 2023 18:15:21 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2023/aug/06/swedish-mountain-lodge-closes-as-stomach-bug-spreads-among-hikers" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2023/aug/07/tv-tonight-adrian-brody-stars-in-second-season-of-big-la-lakers-drama" target="_blank">TV tonight: Adrien Brody stars in second season of big LA Lakers drama</a></h2><div class="description"> Winning Time: The Rise of the Lakers Dynasty returns with the focus on the team’s early-80s triumphs. Plus, bizarre thriller Wolf continues to confuse. Here's what to watch this evening's coverage of the team's early 1980s triumph. Plus, we'll also feature a new episode of Wolf.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Mon, 07 Aug 2023 05:20:31 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2023/aug/07/tv-tonight-adrian-brody-stars-in-second-season-of-big-la-lakers-drama" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2023/aug/07/one-hit-wonder-barbie-world-with-aqua" target="_blank">‘Critics wanted us to be a one-hit-wonder’: back in Barbie world with Aqua</a></h2><div class="descriptio